VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT createQuery\(\s*"[^"]*"\s*\+|createNativeQuery\(\s*"[^"]*"\s*\+|Statement\s+\w+\s*=\s*.*createStatement\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:queryForObject\s*\(.*\?|NamedParameterJdbcTemplate|query\s*\(.*\?|PreparedStatement
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects dynamic SQL/HQL query concatenation patterns.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Spring SQL Query Concatenation Sink.
